name: AIPRO
description: Beyond traditional travel business competitiveness, price competitiveness, and B2C-based travel products, it is a platform that will provide a new experience for travel recommendations, cryptocurrency-based convenient payment, and travel through blockchain technology and reliable contract forms. With this technology, as the travel platform changes and social changes in the future, the AIPRO platform will provide a business that shares unique travel product sales and travel experiences beyond the inherent competitiveness of travel agencies.
